  "recipeInstructions": "1. Place all ingredients in a bowl.\n2. Mix well until all components are evenly distributed.\nNote: This stuffing can be used to fill vine leaves, cabbage leaves, tomatoes, zucchinis, eggplant, bell peppers, and Swiss chard.",
